      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RAINBOW RANGER (6) returns from a spell of nine weeks. Last appeared when he scored by 1.5 metres over 2090m at this track. Will have plenty of admirers. MILLYCENT (4) disappointed backers last time out when sixth, beaten 30 metres, over 2090m at this track. Form prior to that was far better, including a victory over 1609m at this track two starts ago. Meets some strong opposition this time but a return to form is not out of the question. MUZZAME MATE (7) was responsible for a better effort last time out when runner-up over 1680m at Launceston. Should run a big race. SOHO TUXEDO (2) is in the mix following a fourth at his most recent appearance over 1680m at Launceston.",
